## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-159"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> 不应该调用之前将其实现的文档加载完毕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-159"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-160">你可以检测文档通过处理完成加载后<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-160">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-161">下面的示例演示如何从文档中调用的脚本函数[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]应用程序使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-161">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-162">在此示例中，脚本函数没有任何参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-162">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-163">以下是[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-163">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-164">如下所示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]实现调用该脚本函数[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-164">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> 不应该调用之前将其实现的文档加载完毕。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-172"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-173">你可以检测文档通过处理完成加载后<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-173">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-174">不，不要将足够多的参数值传递给所调用的脚本中，如果您不将传递到值参数将具有未定义的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-174">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-175">如果您将太多的参数值传递，则忽略多余的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-175">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-176">下面的示例演示如何通过使用，从应用程序调用脚本函数文档<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-176">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-177">在此示例中，脚本函数需要参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-177">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-178">以下是实现将从调用的脚本函数的文档[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-178">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-179">如下所示[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]中函数的实现来调用脚本[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-179">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-193">调用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>具有相同的效果与设置<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-193">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> 标记由开发人员想要以声明方式指定的初始文档的<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>导航到时<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>初始化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-194"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-195">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29>方法可导航到可能包括转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-195">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-196">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>方法可导航到<xref:System.Uri>其中不包括转义符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-197">下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>通过导航到文档<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-197">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-215">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>方法可导航到可能包括转义符的 URL。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-215">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c845a-216">使用<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>方法可导航到<xref:System.Uri>其中不包括转义符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c845a-217">下面的示例演示如何导航到文档并通过指定在新的浏览器窗口中打开它"有关： 空白"目标。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c845a-217">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
